DTSTART:20260629T203000Z
DTEND:20260629T223000Z
SUMMARY:Construction Simulator | Ep. 37 - Everything Is Within Tolerance
 If You Stop Measuring
DESCRIPTION:Back on site for another evening of heavy machinery, large
 projects, and construction techniques that would probably concern actual
 engineers. Construction Simulator is back - bigger and better than ever!
 Take charge of over 70 machines, dozens of them brand new to the
 franchise, and build to your heart's content on two huge maps - on your
 own or with your friends!
URL:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=b192Jgt_yG4
CATEGORIES:Construction Simulator
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:stream-23762211@dr-ravenholm
DTSTAMP:20260609T010000Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260703T233600Z
DTSTART:20260630T203000Z
DTEND:20260630T223000Z
SUMMARY:Dune: Awakening | Ep. 27 - Hubert Can Smell Fear. Good Thing I
 Have None
DESCRIPTION:Arrakis remains dangerous, sandy, and deeply invested in
 ending my survival career. Thankfully, confidence counts for something...
 right? Rise from survival to greatness and challenge the power of an
 Imperium in Dune: Awakening, a brand-new open world survival and crafting
 game. Alone or together with others, you must survive the sandworm, build
 a home, craft your ornithopter, and unravel the story of the missing
 Fremen.
URL:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-WNcVUsHnRE
CATEGORIES:Dune: Awakening
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
