UID:stream-23772211@dr-ravenholm
DTSTAMP:20260610T010000Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260703T233600Z
DTSTART:20260701T203000Z
DTEND:20260701T223000Z
SUMMARY:Sniper Elite III | Ep. 6 - Kasserine Pass
DESCRIPTION:The campaign continues with another mission demanding
 patience, precision, and the ability to avoid attracting absolutely
 everyone's attention. Sniper Elite 3 is a tactical third-person shooter
 that combines stealth, gameplay choice and genre-defining ballistics with
 huge, open levels and the exotic terrain of World War 2 North Africa.
URL:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=weHIIhZcgjU
CATEGORIES:Sniper Elite III
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:stream-23782211@dr-ravenholm
DTSTAMP:20260611T010000Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260703T233600Z
DTSTART:20260702T203000Z
DTEND:20260702T223000Z
SUMMARY:I Am Fish | Ep. 6 - Aquarium Today, Orbit Tomorrow
DESCRIPTION:Physics once again files for annual leave as our fishy heroes
 continue their increasingly ambitious journey toward freedom... and
 apparently space travel. I Am Fish is a charming, physics-based adventure
 starring four intrepid fish friends, forcibly separated from their home in
 a pet shop fish tank. Swim, fly, roll and chomp your way to the open ocean
 in a bid for freedom and to re-unite once again.
URL:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PZCgYfjyrD4
CATEGORIES:I Am Fish
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
